posting_body: ['Reserve at Bucklin Hill', '1255 Northwest Mirage Lane, Silverdale, WA, 98383', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'An Escape in the Northwest.', 'The Best of the Puget Sound.', 'An Oasis in Beautiful Silverdale', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 675 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Reserve at Bucklin Hill offers a new style of living, tucked away into the best parts of the Pacific Northwest.', 'Located in Silverdale, WA, our 1, 2 and 3-bedroom homes offer an uncommon connection to the beauty of the Northwest outdoors and the buzz of urban life.', 'With warm, newly renovated apartment homes, it truly is a place to press your recharge button.', 'Welcome home to the Reserve at Bucklin Hill!', 'Features', '- Breakfast Bar', '- Stainless steel appliances', '- Large Closets', '- Wood burning fireplaces', '- Patio or Lanai', '- Granite', 'Community Amenities', '- Community Garden', '- Spa/Hot Tub', '- Outdoor patio with Gas Grilling and lounge seating', '- Great room with stone fireplace', '- Heated Swimming Pool', '- State of the art fitness center', '- Complimentary Electric Car Charging', '- New Playground', '- Basketball Court', '- Business Center', '- Scenic nature trails', '- Package Receiving Hub', '- New Outdoor sport court', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday 9:00 am to 6:00 pm', 'Saturday 10:00 am to 5:00 pm', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - allowed 2 per household', 'Income Requirements:', 'Gross income 2.5 times the monthly rent.', 'JCQzFB8vFfc8']
